description: All right, Atlanta. There is a new rule of the road: keep an eye out for Roti Rolls, because after ruling as the “Best Food Truck” in Charleston, SC for five years in a row, they’re rolling out a brand new truck, just for you. Roti Paratha (AKA a “Pillowy Pocket of Love”) is a warm, doughy, flaky bread that is used to tuck all sorts of toppings into a tasty taco. With a mission to exclusively use locally sourced “farm to truck” ingredients, the fusion-full Roti selection at this truck is all fresh and fantastically flavorful. You just gotta come out and rock a Roti Roll.
name: Roti Rolls Atlanta
